Lance Corporal Rylee J. McCollum, USMC; 

Lance Corporal Dylan R. Merola, USMC; 

Lance Corporal Kareem M. Nikoui, USMC; 

Petty Officer Third Class Maxton W. Soviak, USN; and 

Staff Sergeant Ryan C. Knauss, USA.

This is huge.

@RAFWrestlingUSA will showcase the incredible talent of American wrestlers. Growing up in Bloomsburg and wrestling in high school gyms across PA and then at West Point, this sport hits close to home to me and remains in the bloodstream of Pennsylvania.

Looking forward to tuning in on August 30—and cheering on @penn_state legend @NoBickal!

What an incredible story of courage and resilience.

@PennStateVBall’s Katie Schumacher-Cawley is first Division I female head volleyball coach to win a national title. And she did so while battling cancer with a smile on her face.

A huge congratulations to Coach Katie on receiving the 2025 Jimmy V Award for Perseverance at the @ESPN ESPYs!

When my @Steelers are out, I’m all in for the birds 🦅

@RogerMarshallMD, you’re on. May the best team win. Looking forward to eating some KC BBQ and seeing you sport some @Eagles gear.

#FlyEaglesFly #SuperBowlLIX
